  m_Name: WithSecret
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _NPCName: Howie
  _lines:
  - Ohhhh man, Stardust!!!
  - You drive a hard bargin...
  - Let's see here...
  - I'll take that
  - Aaaaand I'll let you pass
  - I'll even throw in a little treat for you-
  - Well-
  - I suppose it would be for her now!
  - Baked it myself!
  - It's the one you always get for her
  - Beignets!
  - Here-
  - I put it in your pocket for ya!
  - Even if you couldn't find what you bought
  - I'm pretty sure she'd still love this
  - Now go see your girl!
